author: Marcus Cho
title: D.R.A.M. Joins With Urban Outfitters for Exclusive Graphic Long-Sleeve
text:
Visit the original post to see all 4 images from this gallery. 
Following hot on the heels of their Juicy Couture collaboration , Urban Outfitters has just tapped D.R.A.M. for a brand-new exclusive collab.
Using a unisex white long-sleeve as base, Urban Outfitters has opted to utilize D.R.A.M.’s unique personality and sense of style as inspiration for the design. As a whole, the shirt features D.R.A.M. holding his labradoodle/ Big Baby D.R.A.M. album cover star “IDNIT,” (short for “Idnit So Cute”) re-imagined as a Charlie Brown and Snoopy-esque cartoon characters, with a row of pink “D.R.A.M.”s written down both sleeves.
Available for a limited time only, the tee will retail for $38 USD over at Urban Outfitters’ official site .
